{"tid":555007,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【險象環生】廢老推車仔行夏慤道 經紅隧過海去九龍","createTime":"2018-02-09T04:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T10:38:05.000Z","uid":2547,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"34dc42b7e1086196da38dc5e3d0a7d258bb3fd76","tid":555007,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T04:45:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h8CZErmteio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh8CZErmteio&d=g2lStspYMc9BVbsoXhqxw0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=654d337a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h8CZErmteio</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/09/124515_b0811cde755c7e53b910c8ffbd29cdf6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F09%2F124515_b0811cde755c7e53b910c8ffbd29cdf6.png&h=d4bdd97b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上10時11分，紅磡海底隧道的職員，發現一名老婦推着手推車進入管道往九龍方向前行，連忙報警。警員接報到場，在九龍出口截獲老婦，她的手推車上有兩紙箱，警員隨即將她送往灣仔警署作進一步了解，暫列流浪婦人。<br />\n<br />\n有網民之前拍攝到婦人的蹤影，只見她推着手推車，沿灣仔告士打道中線前行，當時巴士、私家車和的士在她兩旁駛過，但她也毫不理會，及後進入紅隧管道，沿慢線的邊旁前行，旁若無人。<br />\n<br />\n徒步闖紅隧事件並非首次，根據法例，任何人未經批准擅自徒步闖入隧道區，可判罰款5,000元及監禁六個月。"},{"pid":"b2322b0eea78e191c71c1a513b405b42c68c8bce","tid":555007,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T04:48:59.000Z","msg":"廢老唔會有事<br />\n港豬裡頭有道德L<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ab035c2a6871ae06b5b20d608c0bafeb35c5ae","tid":555007,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T04:50:42.000Z","msg":"勁過行東廊同過將軍澳道"},{"pid":"bec84ed2faca44c809d8b1f9c23fc48773ca7a31","tid":555007,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T05:10:49.000Z","msg":"下？任過㗎喎 <img src=\"/